      "sc:contributor": [
        "Liesa Salzer",
        "Michael Stravs"
      ],
      "sc:description": "MetaboCoreUtils defines metabolomics-related core functionality provided as low-level functions to allow a data structure-independent usage across various R packages. This includes functions to calculate between ion (adduct) and compound mass-to-charge ratios and masses or functions to work with chemical formulas. The package provides also a set of adduct definitions and information on some commercially available internal standard mixes commonly used in MS experiments.",
      "sc:license": "Artistic-2.0",
      "sc:name": "MetaboCoreUtils",
